  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This assessment evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use is limited to pre-market submission support for a left-ventricular assist device operating at 5 L/min and 3500 RPM; the decision scope covers only the hemolysis index quantity of interest as defined in the accompanying regulatory submission narrative. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed; seven achieved their required levels and six were scoped out at MRL 5 per program agreement. Decision: Accepted with conditions documented in the decision record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-claim-001",
