      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Monte Carlo UQ on all model inputs with PDFs derived from literature or measurement; Sobol sensitivity indices computed; top-3 influential inputs identified.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed with 10,000 samples; Sobol indices computed. Top inputs: hemolysis model exponent (S=0.41), blood viscosity (S=0.28), inlet velocity profile (S=0.19). PDF sources documented. Level 4 not reached due to unquantified impeller surface roughness uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum n=5 independent experimental replicates with inter-sample variability characterised; outlier analysis performed.",
      "rationale": "Only two experimental replicates available from FDA benchmark dataset. Insufficient sample size for statistical characterisation at MRL 5. Epistemic gap flagged."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
