      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between experimental input parameters and computational model inputs; equivalency metric above 0.90 on all primary inputs.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping not completed. Inlet velocity profile assumed fully developed in CFD; experimental profile not characterised. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    }
  ],
